{"tid":2098193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共外交部又想炒車，「建議你關注一下國民的民意」","createTime":"2020-07-07T10:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T19:09:18.000Z","uid":42246,"like":214,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"acc97fd575cbfadd71ef11ddd423a0c54d547a93","tid":2098193,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"2019 10月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1954265617/4426103723124685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F1954265617%2F4426103723124685&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=80cd5551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/1954265617/4426103723124685</a><br />\n<br />\n【#外交部回应央视暂停转播NBA#：中方的立场已经非常清楚了】耿爽：中国驻休斯敦总领馆已经就休斯敦火箭俱乐部有关人士的错误言论向对方提出了严正交涉，中国篮球协会以及休斯敦火箭队的中方合作伙伴都相继发表了声明，中方的立场已经非常清楚了，<span style=\"color: red;\">我建议你去关注一下普通中国民众对此事的反应和他们的态度。跟中方开展交流与合作，却不了解中国的民意，这是行不通的。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國民眾民意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEtYYvk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEtYYvk.jpg&h=ee85a0e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yX7by5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyX7by5H.jpg&h=be851e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n2020 7月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/3901624042/4524112782914438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F3901624042%2F4524112782914438&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=79febf72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/3901624042/4524112782914438</a><br />\n<br />\n【#赵立坚让英方征求英国人民的意见#】7月7日，外交部发言人赵立坚表示，BNO护照持有者有300多万人，英方在做出决定之前，最好要想一想，这些人如果都到了英国，他们要享受跟英国国民一样的工作、医疗、福利待遇。英国政府在做出最终决定之前，<span style=\"color: red;\">最好也要征求一下英国人民的意见，他们是怎么看待这件事的？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又想比人笑多次咩強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d26c85b23d3926514f5c676bf3748a8f9b33bca","tid":2098193,"uid":38904,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"中共重驚過 conservative 喺 parliament 唔夠過半數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a05b8e013a9c856d1533255c6d71cb29ecc639","tid":2098193,"uid":42246,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"關注一下中國人想點先啦 中國外部<br />\n上次比自己人打完兩巴重唔醒少少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570227dbd93c8151a258eb0d2fe13b9c304e7ede","tid":2098193,"uid":362015,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"7d26c85b23d3926514f5c676bf3748a8f9b33bca","tid":2098193,"uid":38904,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"中共重驚過 conservative 喺 parliament 唔夠過半數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"呢家係跨黨支持<br />\n仲要睇youtube留言/facebook<br />\n講緊一面倒支持香港人<br />\nbj/raab仲俾hater讚做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae23cd4a3aad172004e928e1f48bd67505cad5e","tid":2098193,"uid":51583,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"將呢d野推比英國人睇<br />\n又多1成會撐港人"},{"pid":"5c651b4dfbaceb1aafe6cb3c5d421c18e2c79034","tid":2098193,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"